name: Doc Talk: A Deadline and Nō Studios Podcast

episodes.title: 'AUM: The Cult At The End Of The World' Filmmakers
episodes.description: Filmmakers Ben Braun and Chiaki Yanagimoto discuss their documentary AUM: The Cult at the End of the World, an exploration of the Japanese religious movement and doomsday cult responsible for a fatal terror attack on the Toyko subway.
